  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-top-width: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江社团一档写作类社刊，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://st.hujiang.com/mag/135231930/\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0,90,148);\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin-left: 5px; line-height: 1.8em; border-top-width: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江社团订阅本社刊！</p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i3.s.7.hjfile.cn/entry/201605/8bc73f1e-b526-450c-ac4b-cd2e92d25541.jpg\" style=\"font-size: 15px; height: 498px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; width: 500px; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\" /><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWriting: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\tEarphones<br />\n\tEarphones are devices fitted to the ear to receive sound signals. What do the earphones look like? Who is wearing them? Where is the person?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: They put on earphones... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) custom-fit earphones<br />\n\t2) earphones worn by performers in a concert<br />\n\t3) earphones worn by bodyguards<br />\n\t4) earphones worn by news reporter<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tHe had to stay alert and be aware of his surroundings. Wearing both sides of the earphone would block out too much of the ambient noise, making him miss the happenings of his surroundings. It would be dangers when a person crossed the road and did not hear the honking of on-coming traffic. As a rule of thumb, if Wolfe were to wear earphones when outside, he would only put on one side. Wolfe took another sip and looked towards the elevators. There were people exiting the elevators, but the person he was waiting for was not in sight.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/167821523910/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p787970/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p787970\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p794686/\">开口练告别哑巴英语！你真会用英文寒暄吗</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p795147/\">又一铁娘子？卡梅伦力挺的英国新首相何许人</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p794661/\">最近中国大妈承包了英国小镇 居民表示很懵逼</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p794997/\">囧研究：所有英文小说都逃不过这6种套路！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p737543/\">独处≠孤独：学会自我陪伴 更会与人相处</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p794913/\">囧研究 英文名有讲究 哪些很man哪些很小女人</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p794981/\">帅小哥抓拍到棕熊跟他挥手的一瞬间 贼萌！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p795124/\">风靡全球的Pokemon Go 今天你玩了吗？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p794907/\">欧洲杯落幕！C罗哭了！葡萄牙队终于夺冠！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p793717/\">论这些年的神翻译是如何成就一首英文歌的</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http://kr.hujiang.com\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江韩语</a></div><hr style=\"border: 0.5px solid gray;\" />", 
